OL,6,FA speeding driver who caused the death
OL,7,Fof a young woman and seriously injured
OL,8,Ftwo others has been jailed.
OL,10,FMolly Mycroft, 21, of Ivanhoe Road in
OL,11,F, pleaded guilty to causing the death
OL,12,Fof 20-year-old Sarah Oliver by
OL,13,Fdangerous driving and seriously
OL,14,Finjuring two passengers.
OL,16,FOn 2 August 2022, Mycroft was driving
OL,17,Fher Seat Ibiza along Wheatley Hall
OL,18,FRoad in Doncaster, in excess of the
OL,19,F40mph speed limit. She ignored a red
OL,20,Flight and collided with a BMW in which
OL,21,FSarah Oliver was a passenger.
