OL,6,FFootage obtained during the
OL,7,Finvestigation showed Mycroft on her
OL,8,Fmobile phone prior to the collision.
OL,10,FCCTV footage capturing the collision
OL,11,Fshowed how Mycroft failed to stop at
OL,12,Fthe red light that had been on for six
OL,13,Fseconds.
OL,15,FMs Oliver's family said in a
OL,16,Fstatement: "Sarah, our daughter,
OL,17,Fgranddaughter, sister and much-loved
OL,18,Ffriend is missed every day. She was a
OL,19,Fbeautiful young woman who had her
OL,20,Fwhole life ahead of her.
