OL,6,F"Sarah had the ability to light up a
OL,7,Froom. She loved spending time with her
OL,8,Ffamily and was looking forward to
OL,9,Ftravelling and becoming a Godmother to
OL,10,Fher best friend's baby this summer.
OL,12,F"She died six days before her 21st
OL,13,Fbirthday and while we should have been
OL,14,Fplanning celebrations, we were instead
OL,15,Fplanning a funeral; her life and our
OL,16,Flives were taken away from us by
OL,17,Fselfish actions.
OL,19,F"No family should have to go through
OL,20,Fwhat we have endured."
