OL,6,FSgt John Taylor from said: "This is a
OL,7,Ftragic case. The actions of Mycroft
OL,8,Fshowed no regards for the safety of
OL,9,Fothers and resulted in the death of
OL,10,FSarah and two other motorists
OL,11,Fsustaining serious injuries.
OL,13,F"We know Mycroft was using her mobile
OL,14,Fphone whilst driving and that she was
OL,15,Fspeeding at the time of the collision.
OL,16,FI urge people to consider the
OL,17,Fconsequences of these actions."
